des:
Helo app controls and scenes your smart devices at home.

After connecting Alexa to your Helo products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Helo by Strong" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Helo account in our "Helo by Strong" app;
(3). You need to have some Helo devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Helo by Strong" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Helo" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Helo" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Helo", and you'll be navigated to Helo login page;
(9). Input your Helo by Strong account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
* Alexa, turn on kitchen light
* Alexa, turn off kitchen light
* Alexa, dim livingroom light
* Alexa, brighten livingroom light
* Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent
* Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue
